{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-128-hexagonal-tile-differences","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 128: Razlike heksagonalnih pločica","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Šestokutna pločica sa brojem 1 je okružena prstenom od šest šestokutnih pločica, počevši od pozicije sata \"12\" i brojeći pločice od 2 do 7 u smeru suprotnom kazaljci na satu.</p>\n<p>Novi prstenovi se dodaju na isti način, a sledeći prstenovi se broje od 8 do 19, od 20 do 37, od 38 do 61, i tako dalje. Ilustracija ispod prikazuje prvih tri prstena.</p>\n<img alt=\"three first rings of arranged hexagonal tiles with numbers 1 to 37, and with highlighted tiles 8 and 17\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/hexagonal-tile-differences.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Kada pronađemo razliku između pločice $n$ i svakog od njenih šest suseda, definišemo $PD(n)$ kao broj tih razlika koji su premijni brojevi.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako radimo u smeru kazaljke naoklono oko ploče 8, razlike su 12, 29, 11, 6, 1 i 13. Dakle $PD(8) = 3$.</p>\n<p>Slično tome, razlike koje okružuju pločicu 17 su 1, 17, 16, 1, 11 i 10, stoga je $PD(17) = 2$.</p>\n<p>Može se pokazati da najveća vrednost za $PD(n)$ je $3$.</p>\n<p>Ako se sve ćelije koje $PD(n) = 3$ poređaju u rastućem redosledu da formiraju niz, 10. ćelija će biti 271.</p>\n<p>Pronađi pločicu 2000 u ovoj seriji.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3ec1000cf542c50feff","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301755,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-128-hexagonal-tile-differences"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function hexagonalTile(tileIndex) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nhexagonalTile(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>hexagonalTile(10)</code> treba vratiti <code>271</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(hexagonalTile(10), 271);"},{"text":"<p><code>hexagonalTile(2000)</code> treba da vrati <code>14516824220</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(hexagonalTile(2000), 14516824220);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-128-hexagonal-tile-differences","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-129-repunit-divisibility","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-127-abc-hits","id":"5900f3ec1000cf542c50feff","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-128-hexagonal-tile-differences"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}